Execute `cargo clean` or similar commands specific to the language on all projects

Usage: clean [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -d, --dry-run
          Run the program without making any changes

  -e, --exclude <EXCLUDE>
          Exclude specific projects (by name)

  -l, --language <LANGUAGE>
          Language to filter by

          Possible values:
          - node-js: `NodeJS` projects (with `node_modules` folder)
          - rust:    `Rust` projects (with `target` folder)

  -p, --path <PATH>
          Path to a directory

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')

  -V, --version
          Print version
